-- DDL for table INL.KONTO

CREATE TABLE INL.KONTO (
    FIRMA DECIMAL(6,0) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.0,
    KUNDEKONTO DECIMAL(6,0) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.0,
    KONTOTYPE DECIMAL(3,0) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.0,
    OPPRETTET_DATO DECIMAL(8,0) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.0,
    OPPSAGT_DATO DECIMAL(8,0) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.0,
    MERKNAD VARCHAR(256),
    SALDO DECIMAL(13,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.0,
    TIDSPUNKT TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT TIMESTAMP,
    BRUKERID CHARACTER NOT NULL DEFAULT ' '
);
